{"id":359,"date":"2024-05-10T06:08:53","date_gmt":"2024-05-10T06:08:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/?p=359"},"modified":"2024-05-10T06:08:53","modified_gmt":"2024-05-10T06:08:53","slug":"flipkart-grid-4-0-software-development-challenge","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/flipkart-grid-4-0-software-development-challenge\/","title":{"rendered":"Flipkart Grid 4.0 Software Development Challenge"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-rank-math-toc-block\" id=\"rank-math-toc\" id=\"rank-math-toc\"><p>Table of Contents<\/p><nav><ul><li ><a href=\"#flipkart-grid-4-0\">Flipkart Grid 4.0 <\/a><\/li><li ><a href=\"#requirements-and-team-rules\">Requirements and Team Rules <\/a><\/li><li ><a href=\"#stages-and-hackathons-in-g-ri-d-4-0\">Stages and Hackathons In  GRiD 4.0<\/a><\/li><li ><a href=\"#rewards-and-prices\">Rewards and Prices <\/a><\/li><li ><a href=\"#faq-flipkart-grid-4-0-software-development-challenge\"> FAQ &#8211; Flipkart Grid 4.0 Software Development Challenge<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"flipkart-grid-4-0\">Flipkart Grid 4.0 <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Flipkart Grid 4.0: This Software development challenge organized by Flipkart is providing a golden opportunity to meet important challenges through technology expertise. Flipkart Grid 4.0 in the year 2022 has developed its fourth edition and getting bigger by throwing real-world challenges from the e-commerce industry to the world&#8217;s top engineers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hence in the past years, Flipkart allowed students from various domains to participate and win different prizes. Moreover, this will help students to get a full-time job and internship from Flipkart.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"requirements-and-team-rules\">Requirements and Team Rules <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The latest requirements for Flipkart Grid 4.0 is as follows:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Students appearing for B.tech \/B.E\/B.S\/M.Tech\/M.S. or equivalent Engineering programs (Batch 2023,2024,2025 &amp;2026) from engineering colleges in India and the United States can participate.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Participants must be divided into groups of two or three.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Batch 2022 is not eligible to contest this challenge.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Students belonging to any specialization can participate.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Full-time  students only allowed<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>One participant should belong to one team<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>If any changes to the above-mentioned rules, participants will be disqualified from the team. <\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>  The registration timeline for Flipkart Grid  4.0 is between  3rd June 2022, 07:00 PM, and 8th September.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"stages-and-hackathons-in-g-ri-d-4-0\">Stages and Hackathons In  GRiD 4.0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Level 1: E-Commerce &amp; Tech Quiz<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Every team will get a set of questions to answer in 30 minutes. These questions will be focused on E-commerce and Technology(Technology Awareness + Techstack &amp;Computer science basics)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Criteria for E-Commerce &amp; Tech Quiz round  following:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Every registered team must complete the online test<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A team should take part will all its players.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A score according to the average score of team members will be provided.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Every team member doesn&#8217;t have to take part in the team.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>All teams will attend the quiz simultaneously when the quiz window is opened.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Depending upon the accuracy and speed, each participant will be ranked. Whereas, if two teams got the same score, the team who completed first will be ranked more.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Every Participating team will move to the next level depending on their score.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Deadline is between July 1st, 2022 and 3rd July,2022, 12:30 PM IST <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Problem Statement Preference Selection for GRiD 4.0<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Level 1 selected teams must submit their preferences for the problem statements. Teams will be assigned problems based on their preferences and Level 1 scores. The problem statements are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>MetaCommerce &#8211; The Future of Shopping with Metaverse.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Blockchain-based eCommerce Warranty System using NFTs.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Extract Trends from social media data.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Level 2: Proof of Concept with Demo Video and Code submission<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Level 1 teams can submit their Idea Brief and video for Idea Submission anytime before the round&#8217;s deadline during the challenge window.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Criteria for  Submission of Proof of Concept with Demo Video and Code submission round are the following.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>The shortlisted team of Level 1 will move to Level 2. <\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Level 1 shortlisted teams move on to Level 2 and receive problem statements based on their chosen domain. <\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Each team gets a unique problem statement. <\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Teams can submit their work anytime until the level&#8217;s deadline during the challenge term. <\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The goal is to present a working proof of concept, along with a sample video and source code. Advancement to the next level is based on team performance in Level 2 of Grid 4.0.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The deadline starts from 13th June 2022, 07:00 PM to 1st August 2022, 06:00 AM IST <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Level 3: The National Finale<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The final participants will be given chance to show their solutions to flipkart panel of domain experts at the Grid 4.0 final level. The deadline for this is from 8th September 2022 to 8th September 2022, 08:00 PM.  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"rewards-and-prices\">Rewards and Prices <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Win appealing prizes and get a chance to join tech internships and full-time positions through Grid 4.0.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Internship Stipend: INR 1,00,000 per month.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>SDE-1 Role Compensation: INR 32.57 LPA.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Prizes <\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Winners: EGVs worth INR 1,50,000.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>First Runners-up: EGVs worth INR 75,000.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Top 50 teams in Level 1 Quiz: GRiD goodies.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Note: Prize amount for foreign competitors is subject to currency conversion rate at the time of distribution. All salaries and prizes are subject to change.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Certificates <\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A certificate of merit will be provided<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Level 1 qualified teams<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Top 20 teams per college <\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Finalist<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"faq-flipkart-grid-4-0-software-development-challenge\"><br>FAQ &#8211; Flipkart Grid 4.0 Software Development Challenge<\/h2>\n\n\n<div id=\"rank-math-faq\" class=\"rank-math-block\">\n<div class=\"rank-math-list \">\n<div id=\"faq-question-1690802054827\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h3 class=\"rank-math-question \"> Qn 1. What is the last date to apply for Flipkart GRiD 2024?<\/h3>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. Flipkart GRiD 5.0-Software Development Track for 2024, 2025, 2026, 2027 Batch: Last date to\u00a0apply13th July 2023.12-Jun-2023<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1690802137639\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h3 class=\"rank-math-question \">Qn 2. Is there a negative marking in Flipkart GRiD?<\/h3>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. There is no negative marking for this quiz. Only the Team Leader will play the quiz. Every team will get a set of 30 questions to be answered within 30 minutes. Every team will be ranked on accuracy (score) and speed (finish time).<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1690802142871\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h3 class=\"rank-math-question \">Qn 3: What to do in Flipkart GRiD?<\/h3>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans:  GRiD: India&#8217;s No. 1 Engineering Campus Case Competition by Flipkart. Solve real E-Commerce problems with your technical skills and knowledge!<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Flipkart Grid 4.0 Flipkart Grid 4.0: This Software development challenge organized by Flipkart is providing a golden opportunity to meet important challenges through technology expertise. Flipkart Grid 4.0 in the year 2022 has developed its fourth edition and getting bigger by throwing real-world challenges from the e-commerce industry to the world&#8217;s top engineers. Hence in &#8230; <a title=\"Flipkart Grid 4.0 Software Development Challenge\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/flipkart-grid-4-0-software-development-challenge\/\" aria-label=\"More on Flipkart Grid 4.0 Software Development Challenge\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":4796,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[13,28],"tags":[88,89,90],"class_list":["post-359","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-computer-science","category-cpp-programming","tag-flipkart-grid-4-0-software-development-challenge","tag-grid4-0","tag-hackathon","generate-columns","tablet-grid-50","mobile-grid-100","grid-parent","grid-33"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/359"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"